{"lemma":"عَفِيف","slug":"عَفِيف","root":"ع.ف.ف","root_slug":"ع-ف-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ف-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun_prop","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n29703"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%81"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"chaste, pure, virtuous"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"decent"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"righteous"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʕa.fiːf/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n29703","headword_ar":"عَفِيفٌ","root":"Ef","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaf~N","text_ar":"عَفٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"epithets from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaf~a","text_ar":"عَفَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as such signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Abstaining"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K) from what is unlawful, (S, O,) or from what is not lawful nor comely or decorous, (K,) or from things that should be sacred or inviolable, and base, or carnal, objects of inordinate desire, (TA,) or from a thing: (Msb:) [and very often used as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abstinent, continent, chaste, virtuous, modest, decent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"decorous:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] fem. of the former with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, K;) and so of ↓ the latter, (S, O, Msb, K,) which has no broken pl.: (TA:) the pl. masc. (of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EafiyfN","text_ar":"عَفِيفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", Msb, TA) is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEif~aA='u","text_ar":"اَعِفَّا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, Msb, K, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEif~apN","text_ar":"اَعِفَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb, TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EafiyfapN","text_ar":"عَفِيفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to a woman, signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excellent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"high-born, good, righteous,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"virtuous;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [more commonly]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"continent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chaste;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) and the pl. of this is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EafaAy^ifu","text_ar":"عَفَايِفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EafiyfaAtN","text_ar":"عَفِيفَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}